"/Big_Chest\" title=\"Big Chest\">Big Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Big_Stone_Chest\" title=\"Big Stone Chest\">Big Stone Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Chest\" title=\"Chest\">Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Junimo_Chest\" title=\"Junimo Chest\">Junimo Chest</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Fridge\" title=\"Mini-Fridge\">Mini-Fridge</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Chest\" title=\"Stone Chest\">Stone Chest</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Signs\" title=\"Crafting\">Signs</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dark_Sign\" title=\"Dark Sign\">Dark Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Stone_Sign\" title=\"Stone Sign\">Stone Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Text_Sign\" title=\"Text Sign\">Text Sign</a> • <a href=\"/Wood_Sign\" title=\"Wood Sign\">Wood Sign</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Crafting#Misc\" title=\"Crafting\">Misc</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Anvil\" title=\"Anvil\">Anvil</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee_Maker\" title=\"Coffee Maker\">Coffee Maker</a> • <a href=\"/Cookout_Kit\" title=\"Cookout Kit\">Cookout Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Deconstructor\" title=\"Deconstructor\">Deconstructor</a> • <a href=\"/Fairy_Dust\" title=\"Fairy Dust\">Fairy Dust</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Computer\" title=\"Farm Computer\">Farm Computer</a> • <a href=\"/Hopper\" title=\"Hopper\">Hopper</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Forge\" title=\"Mini-Forge\">Mini-Forge</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Jukebox\" title=\"Mini-Jukebox\">Mini-Jukebox</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Shipping_Bin\" title=\"Mini-Shipping Bin\">Mini-Shipping Bin</a> • <a href=\"/Sewing_Machine\" title=\"Sewing Machine\">Sewing Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Staircase\" title=\"Staircase\">Staircase</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Blessings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414151340\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.132 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.147 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1380/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16120/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1780/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1816/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 517 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   74.180      1 -total\n 56.20%   41.691      1 Template:Infobox_cooking\n 26.79%   19.872      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 26.41%   19.588      1 Template:Description\n 19.08%   14.154      2 Template:Name\n  6.79%    5.036      2 Template:History\n  4.49%    3.334      4 Template:Price\n  4.31%    3.196      2 Template:Version\n  2.99%    2.218      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  1.73%    1.280      1 Template:NavboxEquipment\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2518-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414151340 and revision id 191196\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "<onlyinclude>{{{{{1|Infobox cooking}}}\n|name        = Deluxe Speed-Gro\n|image       = Deluxe Speed-Gro.png\n|description = {{Description|Deluxe Speed-Gro}}\n|source      = [[Pierre's General Store|Pierre's]] in Year 2+ • [[Oasis]] on Thursdays • [[Crafting]] • [[Bone Mill]] • [[Desert Festival]]\n|sellprice   = 40\n|recipe      = [[File:Farming Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Farming]] Level 8\n|ingredients = {{Name|Oak Resin|1}}{{Name|Bone Fragment|5}}\n|produces    = 5 Deluxe Speed-Gro per craft\n|qiseasoning = false\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Deluxe Speed-Gro''' is a [[Fertilizer]] that speeds [[Crops|crop]] growth by 25% (or a total of 35% with the [[Skills#Farming|Agriculturist Profession]]).<ref name=\"speedincrease\" /> It can be [[Crafting|crafted]] or purchased from [[Pierre's General Store]] for {{Price|150}} from Year 2 onward, or purchased from the [[Oasis]] for {{Price|80}} on Thursdays. Ten Deluxe Speed-Gro may also be received as a gift at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]]. Up to 100 Deluxe Speed-Gro may be purchased from [[Demetrius]]' [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|2|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s each. Ten to twenty Deluxe Speed-Gro may be received from opening a [[Mystery Box]] or [[Golden Mystery Box]].\n\nDeluxe Speed-Gro can be placed on tilled soil ''before or after'' planting a seed, or at any stage of crop growth. It does not reduce time between harvests for multi-harvest crops.\n\nApplying Deluxe Speed-Gro days after planting a seed still decreases the time it takes to fully grow, but it reduces a fixed amount of days per stage for each crop regardless of the day it's applied, and the reduction in stages that the crop has already passed will not retroactively apply. Combined with the fact that the reduction disproportionately affects earlier stages more, this means that its reduction to the rest of the growth time is much lower than the advertised percentage of 25%.<ref name=\"speedincrease2\" />\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|dislike=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nDeluxe Speed-Gro is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nDeluxe Speed-Gro can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|High-Waisted Shirt]].  [[File:Shirt175.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\nDeluxe Speed-Gro is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"speedincrease\">See <samp>StardewValley.TerrainFeatures.HoeDirt::applySpeedIncreases</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n<ref name=\"speedincrease2\">The change in phaseDays in <samp>HoeDirt::applySpeedIncreases</samp> is static regardless of the date of fertilizer application relative to the date of planting. This means that applying fertilizer after planting only affects the current stage and any stages thereafter, in the same way that applying at the same day as planting affects those stages.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Deluxe Speed-Gro now has an effect if used after planting a seed. Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Now requires 5 [[Bone Fragment]]s instead of 1 [[Coral]] to craft. Now sold by [[Demetrius]] during the [[Desert Festival]]. Added as possible prize from [[Mystery Box]]es and [[Golden Mystery Box]]es.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Fertilizer]]\n\n[[de:Luxus-Geschwind-Wachs]]\n[[es:Acelerador deluxe]]\n[[fr:Engrais de croissance rapide II]]\n[[it:Crescipresto deluxe]]\n[[ja:グングンノビールデラックス]]\n[[ko:디럭스 성장 촉진제]]\n[[hu:Luxus gyorsnövesztő]]\n[[pt:Solo Foliar Premium]]\n[[ru:СкороРост Делюкс]]\n[[tr:Üstün Hızlı-Ek]]\n[[zh:高级生长激素]]"
    }
